data.description:
New price, new paint and new carpet. Seller is offering $5000 towards a water heater, refinishing of  the hardwood floors and air duct cleaning. Explore the potential of this fixer-upper to unlock your dream home. Amid a tranquil neighborhood, it presents a canvas for creative transformation. Despite needing attention, its strategic location, spacious layout, and unique features promise an exceptional outcome. Features: 
1) Prime Location: Access schools, parks, shopping, and transit from this serene community. 
2) Ample Space: With a generous layout, diverse design options can be explored. 
3) Reviving History: Original elements like hardwood flooring add to its charm. 4) Outdoor Oasis: The fenced private backyard could become an outdoor haven. 
5) Investment Potential: Beyond a home, it offers enticing investment prospects.
